  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/731bead6b3c505a6c7eca6809b3660b9.avif?t=1768361572\" width=1560 height=336 /></span><br>After Diego return to his world, Luxus, Zafir, and Fin carry on their peaceful life in Burning Horns. However, in one of Zafir's expeditions, the old wizard disappears and Fin decided to rescue him with Luxus's help. Embark on this journey in Luxus' shoes and have the opportunity to fall in love with one of them. You don't need to be familiar with Burning Horns: A Bara Isekai JRPG to understand this new story even though the first game can give you a complete notion about some of the places the characters mention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/a50c6f385883f2be4e4f39f063caee9d.avif?t=1768361572\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Choice System </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Unique Endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Polyamorous Ending</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Game Gallery</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Around 1~2 hours of gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Steam Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/58ad9912eb8f2059bebd1f367c01a394.avif?t=1768361572\" width=1560 height=80 /></span>Bara, BxB, Polyamorous, Muscle, Gay, Multiple Endings</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/731bead6b3c505a6c7eca6809b3660b9.avif?t=1768361572\" width=1560 height=336 /></span><br>After Diego return to his world, Luxus, Zafir, and Fin carry on their peaceful life in Burning Horns. However, in one of Zafir's expeditions, the old wizard disappears and Fin decided to rescue him with Luxus's help. Embark on this journey in Luxus' shoes and have the opportunity to fall in love with one of them. You don't need to be familiar with Burning Horns: A Bara Isekai JRPG to understand this new story even though the first game can give you a complete notion about some of the places the characters mention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/a50c6f385883f2be4e4f39f063caee9d.avif?t=1768361572\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Choice System </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Unique Endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f99c7fb.webp?t=1768361572\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Polyamorous Ending</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228340/extras/8e0601948731069d3035cd496f9